{"tid":1217434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期置頂] 6.15 反送中大遊行","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:24:12.000Z","uid":7948,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d68678cf1b143f0417ccd4dce8773d1dbee738e3","tid":1217434,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oq4L8A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oq4L8A.png&h=4a2b5bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發動連登力量，分享出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296722ade4d20abd58f27e698a3a7f29b4bb1dbd","tid":1217434,"uid":7948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:58:59.000Z","msg":"大家唔好打飛機住<br />\n做咗要做嘅野先"},{"pid":"bf6be39d0606c197aaa6ab82f9e858f81514976a","tid":1217434,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"我地應該要接受香港和理非佔大多數呢個事實，大多數人都唔會衝始終法律後果太重，所以大家可以用合法方式全力阻止惡法，只要係合法渠道去反送中，我相信唔少人都唔介意做多兩步，有啲人可能覺得有啲和理非行動聽起上嚟好似好膠，但請唔好理人點做，只要記住大家都係反送中嘅同路人，我地就應該尊重同埋支持佢地，支持和理非不斷以各種合法途徑反送中。去爭取更多市民同國際社會反送中。唔好話無用，你去做起碼仲有1%會成功，完全唔做就絕對唔會成功。大家一定要盡自己可以承受到嘅所有後果同力量，以政府徹回逃犯條例為成功目標。請記住，唔好再鬧分化，和理非有和理非做，其他人有其他人做，兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n<br />\n歷史例子：<br />\n柏林圍牆冧之前幾個月冇人會覺得有生之年可以見到冧牆嘅一日，03年23條同12年國教都冇人會覺得可以令政府撤回23條同國教，正如今次亦都冇人會覺得可以令政府撤回逃犯條例。<span style=\"color: red;\">再強調一次，唔好話無用，你去做起碼仲有1%會成功，完全唔做就絕對唔會成功。</span>"},{"pid":"1b2ea5492452457d5512133fed0937a0390ad5b9","tid":1217434,"uid":7948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"不篤灰"},{"pid":"4fd7abce5c2abd769492427241ddc591e70e4aca","tid":1217434,"uid":7948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"不割席"},{"pid":"bd4d89fdb5c29b9c89b57ce6f4d2e5da6993a7aa","tid":1217434,"uid":41269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"616定615，好亂"},{"pid":"8dbb4cf0e2bcf72c273903c64ac3c9855fae1641","tid":1217434,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"推吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d5f74848a66a840821061546787ad85550030d","tid":1217434,"uid":219369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"星期日和理非爭下游離票？"},{"pid":"32e053b53ac4b30b9f4fcc4222bf6348b6a83216","tid":1217434,"uid":36470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"團結就是力量"},{"pid":"276ddf658f80c89e60f45395a0f4c6553959946c","tid":1217434,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd4d89fdb5c29b9c89b57ce6f4d2e5da6993a7aa","tid":1217434,"uid":41269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"616定615，好亂"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"615 遊行,616罷工/罷課"},{"pid":"4eac26a9cd5d6c9809e80da8c0a69b63a38e9961","tid":1217434,"uid":210964,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"6月15 星期六黎啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8786fa0ae63be68c88dfea151245fc0517271e4c","tid":1217434,"uid":41269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"276ddf658f80c89e60f45395a0f4c6553959946c","tid":1217434,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd4d89fdb5c29b9c89b57ce6f4d2e5da6993a7aa","tid":1217434,"uid":41269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"616定615，好亂"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"615 遊行,616罷工/罷課"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"ok thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee1b7f705c382f418c2d5e412846e8cfd354b64","tid":1217434,"uid":41269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"屌你星期日擺乜工呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb46a4fbef608b31ffe58f034098ab85176066d","tid":1217434,"uid":146069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"16/6星期日"},{"pid":"b0caa19fa6a83c2c822fb87410d0d5d68de3518c","tid":1217434,"uid":215900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"615 星期六"},{"pid":"1e9bbbb658cf18f825b46779d7344e2bed2f7bd4","tid":1217434,"uid":9076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:03:05.000Z","msg":"好亂啊"},{"pid":"7f208f09756936441bd0e513aa8108d29122340c","tid":1217434,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"開過新post啦"},{"pid":"95aed0168011676f571a91b15ac77f7ec35328f3","tid":1217434,"uid":221049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"15號係星期六，16號係星期日，17號係星期一<br />\n<br />\n所以，應該係616遊行，617三罷"},{"pid":"9a3a6bab003b14c1161d3c3d2b443ec0f59daa49","tid":1217434,"uid":69145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ce5ffa45d6ef1e3bfcb69731d88250135e483d","tid":1217434,"uid":31173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"屌你星期六定星期日架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708cf149c91c89eeb359444e3ff7a3295387fc51","tid":1217434,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"個個星期日，遊行要持之以恆，唔好林住幾個月可以完事，個日一百萬人遊行林鄭已經慌左，所以先死頂想今日格硬搞二三讀，我地如果每個星期遊行，林鄭都好難同雜種交待佢有幾打得，我唔排擠激進運動❨我12/6都有去❳，但衝擊始終係短計，需要長計支援。<br />\n<br />\n首先，衝唔衝得過警察係問題，人地有gas有炮，我地真係好難打得過，其次如果我地打低晒啲警察，北京就有藉口收返香港維持治安，軍隊一黎直接會用實彈，唔會再同你玩橡膠彈同tear gas (甚至可能用毒氣)，到時我地淨係紀念義士都有排忙。<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法嘅好處係大家都會相對安全，又唔犯法，而且可以得到廣泛市民支持、甚至參與，班中年佬你估佢地真係支持今次修例？修例一過，美國一出手，佢地一層樓至少跌一球，星期日遊行佢地就好大機會會肯出黎。反正係長期抗爭，我亦鼓勵大家試多幾次連續超過五十萬人和平遊行，個幾次唔搞激進，敢樣先唔會有機會比政府同建制轉移重點，比位佢地話示威者暴力，所以警方先點點點，回應傳媒個陣只能夠直接回應有市民不滿呢個point。<br />\n<br />\n啲不合作活動可以平時進行，啲激進活動就係星期日遊行後隨機進行，有時搞有時唔搞，可能一個月係一次，但唔知邊個星期日，等啲警犬個個星期日都要ot stand by，我地唔去玩，佢地都一齊冇得放假去玩，玩到佢地謝。<br />\n<br />\n淨係斬一刀落個人度，個人可以去睇下醫生，休養完冇事。但如果成日間唔中攞支針吉下佢，長期落黎，佢真係會崩潰。一個星期日梗係無用，但半年、一年呢？就好難講。有冇睇黃子華，混食係香港人核心價値，叫人長期日日唔返工返學，有幾多人采你？爭取每次都過五十萬人上街遊行先行長遠之計，就算當中四十九萬人唔打得都睇啊。而且出黎多幾，多啲社會參與，佢地對抗爭嘅睇法亦可能轉。以小博大係無得急功近利。<br />\n東德南韓法國都有呢類例子，唔使下下過百萬人，每星期都幾十萬人已經唔野少，和平遊行亦可以吸引多啲和理非出黎參與，喚醒沉默大多數走出黎係首要，佢地係勇武派合理性嘅基礎，勇武同和理非必須合作，雙管齊下。<br />\n<br />\n同埋一定要有啲遊行係個日純理性，除左啲和理非唔采你仲話返你轉頭之外，亦係展示緊比外界睇明顯有兩種唔同類型嘅人都一齊反對，做勢好重要。<br />\n<br />\n今個星期日遊行要純和平理性，呢個係長期抗爭，睇長遠啲，呢次係建立清晰稱定民意基礎嘅好機會，唔好趕走和理非，勇武留返開會日。<br />\n個個星期日遊行，直到林鄭撤回修例同下台為此！"},{"pid":"0f5fb544817a14191447b7c818a838726f5626d8","tid":1217434,"uid":196745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"276ddf658f80c89e60f45395a0f4c6553959946c","tid":1217434,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd4d89fdb5c29b9c89b57ce6f4d2e5da6993a7aa","tid":1217434,"uid":41269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"616定615，好亂"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"615 遊行,616罷工/罷課"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:12:51.000Z","msg":"616星期日黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21d00ad4f2ff1c90c66314f63c23d06d23b3a4e","tid":1217434,"uid":209481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"唔係16遊行咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de103cafd471e0568e338b0fee21d20586bf337c","tid":1217434,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T1